Can we have a wedding every year ?! Reminiscing on this magical day ✨ getting married in this desert was a dream, I felt like my gypsy dreams were coming true. Having my legendary grandfather walk me down the aisle was truly special.

This year has been the fastest of my life. 
-Moved cross country.
-Taken more flights this year than any other year.
-Worked my booty off.
-Drank more coffee than any other year.
-Had one of the highest highs of my life followed by one of the lowest lows.
-Saw my family more days this year than in the last 10 years. 
I am one blessed gata flaca, I can’t wait to see what 2023 has in store ! Sending many blessings to you and yours today and always. 
-Camila Concepcion Aquino

Soap opera chronicles #2
Words.words.words.
Here at Soaps we can’t seem to have enough of so many wordsssss! 13 years this September of Days of our lives for this cubanita! More fun inside looks coming ! #dialogue #setlife #lines #anactorprepares

Soap opera chronicle #3 : Everyone is always shocked we have no crafty on set. Since I started working on soaps in 2008 I have never seen crafty on the two soap sets I have been on. So WE MAKE OUR OWN! Gotta have snacks and drinks in our dressing rooms! #nocrafty #notaregularset #welp #snacks #doordash

Soap opera chronicles #4 
Going to a “normal set” and seeing that you only have 2 to 3 scenes that day, then going on days of our lives and seeing you have between 60 to 75 scenes a day.

#itaintthesame #factory #setlife #notnormal
